22.105Z", "title": "Minneapolis spokesman", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn83025247/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2022270778/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1934", "dates": ["[1934 TO 2000]"], "description": ["Weekly Began with volume 1, number 1 (August 10, 1934); ceased with vol. 65, no. 29 (Dec. 30/Jan. 5, 2000). \"Black newspaper.\" Available on microfilm from the Minnesota Historical Society. Merged with: St. Paul recorder, to form: Minnesota spokesman-recorder. Tone, a picture magazine, appears at infrequent intervals with the newspaper. Volume 1, Number 1 (August 10, 1934); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed November 23, 2022). Thirtieth Year, No. 23 (December 26, 1963) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed November 23, 2022). St. Paul recorder 2835-0944 (DLC) 2022270777 (OCoLC)1351605616 Minnesota spokesman-recorder"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:07.154Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2022270778/", "image_url": [], "index": 13, "language": ["english"], "location": ["hennepin county", "hennepin", "minneapolis", "minnesota", "united states"], "number": ["online resource", "2835-0979", "1351607674", "2022270777", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2022270778"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "minneapolis spokesman (minneapolis, minnesota) 1934-2000 [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 74.31891, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["african american", "african americans", "hennepin county", "hennepin county (minn.)", "hennepin", "minneapolis", "newspapers", "minnesota", "minneapolis (minn.)", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:06:42.779Z", "title": "Minneapolis spokesman", "type": ["title"], "url": "https:/